Former presidents, Olusegun Obasanjo and Goodluck Jonathan are in a closed-door meeting.   A twitter handle, @bolanle_cole shared photos showing the former presidents chatting with a caption, “In the early hours of this morning, Former President, Obasanjo met with Former President, Dr Goodluck Jonathan in a closed-door meeting.”  The former first lady, Patience Jonathan was also seen in the photos.  See photos below: 